Application Data can be Backed up

playstore_details.title: Wealth Check - Bitcoin Wallet Balance and History
playstore_details.description:
Wealth Check allows you to check balance an history of any bitcoin wallet. Just scan bitcoin address QR code to see all important information like bitcoin balance, fiat balance by current conversation rate, transactions history, etc. All scanned wallets are safely stored on your phone for offline access. You can sort wallets in the favorites list.

Key Features:
 • QR Code Support
 • 20+ currency conversion rates
 • History of scanned wallets
 • Favorites list 
 • Offline support

This project is open source. Feel free to contribute at https://github.com/jurajkusnier/bitcoin-balance-check
playstore_details.summary: Check balance and history of any bitcoin wallet
playstore_details.summaryHTML: Check balance and history of any bitcoin wallet
